issues.title: Bring I-D up to date with Unicode 15.0.0
issues.author: stpeter
issues.body: The most recent version of the document at https://www.ietf.org/archive/id/draft-nemoto-precis-unicode14-00.txt covers Unicode 14.0.0. We need to update the document to cover Unicode 15.0.0 as well.

issues.title: Double-check incompatible code points
issues.author: stpeter
issues.body:
Let's take a closer look at the incompatible code points mentioned in RFC 9233 (and additional incompatible code points between 12.0.0. and 15.0.0). This list should include at least the following code points:

U+0CF1
U+0CF2
U+19DA
U+111C9
U+1734

@fightingnemo feel free to add to this list

We might want to create a separate file listing these code points and others that require manual inspection.
